title: Foo Fighters - Gloria Theater (Live 2-CD) 2011 320ak
description:
Foo Fighters - Gloria Theater (Live 2-CD) 2011 320ak

Exclusive concert, organized by 1Live, a radio station from Cologne. This show was limitted to only 600 people. Tickets weren't sold. You could only win them during a lottery in the radio or a few websites. Too bad a lot of people were unlucky enough to stay at home, including myself. Fortunately, the concert was broadcast live. Still great. I connected my radio with an instrument cable through my guitar Preamp into my PCs soundcard.

 Meanwhile In 2017, the band released a single, "Run", and announced their ninth studio album, Concrete and Gold, which is scheduled for release on September 15, 2017.
While we wait ...
